                               TOPOLOGY DISCOVER
Structures
- net-graph with switches (nodes) and links (edges)
- access table
- link_to_port

Actions
It retrives topology information throgh RYU api every DISCOVERY_PERIOD, hence
updates the structures. In addition, if one of the following ryu events happens,
it doas the same.
        EventSwitchEnter,
        EventSwitchLeave,
        EventPortAdd,
        EventPortDelete,
        EventPortModify,
        EventLinkAdd,
        EventLinkDelete


